2. THIRD-PARTY TERMS OF SERVICE:
This application interacts with Discord's Rich Presence IPC API and queries
Discord's detectable applications API and the Steam Community search API.
By using this software, you acknowledge that these interactions might be subject
to the Terms of Service of the respective platforms. You are solely responsible
for ensuring that your use of this software complies with all applicable ToS.

3. ACCOUNT SAFETY:
The author(s) and contributors of this software shall NOT be held liable for any
