4. DATA PRIVACY:
This software does NOT collect, transmit, or store any personal information,
login credentials, or authentication tokens. All data stays on your local machine.
The application communicates only with Discord's local IPC socket and public APIs
(Discord detectable apps, Steam community search).

5. ORIGINAL WORK:
This is a Linux fork of GeForce NOW Rich Presence by KarmaDevz, rewritten from
Python to Go. The original project is available at:
